---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../utils/constants';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`About Us - ${SITE_CONFIG.title}`}
  description="About Corpnce: Engineering the Intelligence Revolution. Training, SaaS, and Consultancy in Rajajinagar, Bengaluru. Mission, vision, history, and why the industry trusts us."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-black text-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          About <span class="text-yellow-400">Corpnce</span>: Engineering the Intelligence Revolution
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300">
          Bridging human potential and technological advancement through simplicity and specialized rigor
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Intro -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          At Corpnce, we believe that the gap between human potential and technological advancement can only be bridged through simplicity and specialized rigor. Based in Rajajinagar, Bengaluru, Corpnce is an emerging technology powerhouse specializing in <strong class="text-black">Training</strong>, <strong class="text-black">SaaS</strong>, and <strong class="text-black">Consultancy</strong>. We don't just teach technology; we architect the professionals and products that will lead the next era of global industry.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- I. Mission & Vision -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-8 text-black border-b-2 border-yellow-400 pb-3 inline-block">
          I. Our Mission & Vision
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-yellow-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">The Vision</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-2 text-lg">
              "To leave a profound impact on humankind with the aid of Emerging Technologies."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We envision a world where the boundary between intuition and data is thinned, allowing individuals and enterprises to reach peak productivity and efficiency through the ethical application of AI.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-yellow-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">The Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-2 text-lg">
              "To be the best in training and creating ready-to-deploy human resources in the field of emerging technologies."
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our mission is to solve the "unskilled engineer" paradox in India by delivering high-level content, research-driven innovation, and a curriculum that prioritizes Technology Quotient (TQ) over rote learning.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- II. History -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-8 text-black border-b-2 border-yellow-400 pb-3 inline-block">
          II. Our History: From Startup to Talent Foundry
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-4">
          <p>
            Founded in <strong class="text-black">2018</strong>, Corpnce was born out of a critical observation: India produces the world's second-highest number of engineers, yet a vast majority lack the industry-ready skills for the AI era.
          </p>
          <p>
            Starting as an elite training boutique in Rajajinagar, Corpnce quickly evolved. We integrated a <strong class="text-black">Project-Based Learning (PBL)</strong> methodology and became the <strong class="text-black">first in India</strong> to introduce the concept of <strong class="text-black">Technology Quotient (TQ)</strong>â€”a unique metric to evaluate a professional's future technology adaptability.
          </p>
          <p>
            Over the years, we have expanded from a training institute into a multi-vertical organization, launching a <strong class="text-black">SaaS</strong> division for autonomous business tools and a <strong class="text-black">Consultancy</strong> arm that helps global MNCs and startups navigate complex data architectures.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- III. Ethical Covenant -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-8 text-black border-b-2 border-yellow-400 pb-3 inline-block">
          III. The Corpnce Ethical Covenant
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          At Corpnce, ethics are not an elective; they are the foundation of our business. We operate under a strict code of conduct that ensures our growth never comes at the cost of our integrity.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Intellectual Honesty</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              We provide realistic career outlooks. We never promise "guaranteed jobs" as a marketing gimmick; instead, we promise the guaranteed quality of knowledge that makes job offers inevitable.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Radical Transparency</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              Whether in our consultancy fee structures or our training curriculum, we maintain an open-book policy. Clients and students alike know exactly what they are investing in.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Algorithmic Fairness</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              In our training and SaaS development, we place a heavy emphasis on Explainable AI (XAI) and bias mitigation. We teach our students to build models that are fair, transparent, and socially responsible.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">The Batch Integrity Rule</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              To maintain the highest level of mentorship ethics, we strictly limit our batches to 15 students. We value the depth of a single student's success over the volume of a crowded classroom.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- IV. Why the Industry Trusts Us -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-8 text-black border-b-2 border-yellow-400 pb-3 inline-block">
          IV. Why the Industry Trusts Us
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Corpnce stands at the intersection of Research and Industry. Our team, led by a "Wizard of light bulbs" CEO and a "Storytelling Digital Overlord," consists of practitioners who have worked with E&Y, Edge Networks, and global research bodies.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-black text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border-2 border-yellow-400">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">13,500+</div>
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400">Cumulative Teaching Hours</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border-2 border-yellow-400">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">1,000+</div>
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400">Lives Impacted through career transitions</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border-2 border-yellow-400">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">80+</div>
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400">Global Hiring Partners <span class="text-gray-500">(Google, Microsoft, Amazon)</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Location -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-black">Our Location</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-black">
            {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.label}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
            {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.street}
            <br />
            {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.city}, {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.state}{' '}
            {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.zip}
            <br />
            {SITE_CONFIG.contact.address.main.country}
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong class="text-yellow-400">Phone:</strong>{' '}
            <a
              href={`tel:${SITE_CONFIG.contact.phone.india.replace(/\s/g, '')}`}
              class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-500 font-semibold"
            >
              {SITE_CONFIG.contact.phone.india}
            </a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong class="text-yellow-400">Email:</strong>{' '}
            <a
              href={`mailto:${SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}`}
              class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-500 font-semibold"
            >
              {SITE_CONFIG.contact.email}
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="bg-black text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border-2 border-yellow-400">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">
          Join our comprehensive training programs and take your career to the next level.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-primary inline-block"
          onclick="if(window.trackCTAClick) window.trackCTAClick('about_cta', 'about');"
        >
          Contact Us Today
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
